headline: Trane Technologies (TT) Increasing its Footprint in the Data Center Cooling Industry
summary: Trane Technologies Plc (NYSE:TT) is one of the 10 Data Center Cooling Companies to Invest In. On December 4, Trane Technologies Plc’s (NYSE:TT) price target was raised by $11 to $506 by Barclays. The firm maintained the previous Overweight rating on the stock.
